  52:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****     (#) Configure the EXTI line using HAL_EXTI_SetConfigLine().
  53:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Choose the interrupt line number by setting "Line" member from
  54:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  55:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) Configure the interrupt and/or event mode using "Mode" member from
  56:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  57:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) For configurable lines, configure rising and/or falling trigger
  58:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              "Trigger" member from EXTI_ConfigTypeDef structure.
  59:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****         (++) For Exti lines linked to gpio, choose gpio port using "GPIOSel"
  60:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_exti.c ****              member from GPIO_InitTypeDef structure.
